        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This black-and-gray thurible is decorated with a skeleton motif; the jaw of one of the decorative skulls unhinges, allowing you to load it with incense as an action. A long, thin chain is connected to the top of the thurible.",
        "level": 9,
